{
  "text": "Patients. A total of 115 patients enrolled in the ACT DMD trial were randomized to placebo. [CITATION_1] The ITT population for the placebo arm consisted of 114 patients, with 53 patients receiving deflazacort and 61 receiving prednisone/prednisolone. One patient with a valid post-baseline 6MWD was discontinued because gene sequencing did not confirm the presence of a nonsense mutation in the dystrophin gene.",
  "correct_citation": {
